oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Girl in clover
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: A black and white photograph of an unidentified girl, wearing a sweater, skirt, and bow with a pearl necklace, seated in button clover, in front of a barn located in Wilson County, Tenn. She is holding a clump of clover in one hand.
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:source: Tennessee Department of Conservation Photograph Collection, 1937-1976
